data.title: College Visit
data.text: We stopped here after our college visit to U.K.  It's a nice place with a lot to choose from. A bit pricey though.

data.title: Great place for UK gear
data.text:
In town for a UK softball game. Selection of UK gear for sale at the game was minimal so we asked around and were directed here.

Short drive from the stadium. Several free parking spots located behind the store.

Huge selection of fan gear. We were able to purchase shirts, mugs, hats, and more. Clerks were helpful and friendly. 
Will certainly stop back in when we are in town.
